|  *~Description~*                                                      |
|  >><<>><<>><<>><                                                      |
|      Tsuushin Taisen Logic Battle Daisessen (in English this means    |
|     "Communication War Logic Battle Snow Fight") is a simple game     |
|      of guessing~ This game is very similar to that of the popular    |
|      board-game called "Battle Ship". You must strategically place    |
|      your army on your playing field (you can choose each persons'    |
|      formation... such as singular, groups of three, four, etc.)      |
|      in order to try to confuse your opponent. This game is played    |
|      with two players (vs. human, or vs. CPU) and each player must    |
|      attack the other players board in order to uncover their         |
|      hidden army. Each move is timed, so you must act quickly! You    | 
|      can use a special strategy too~ Once it is your turn, you can    |
|      see the opponents playing field, and the places where you        |
|      have attacked are shown. If there is a white X, that is a        |
|      MISS, so you should not attack that area again. If there is a    |
|      green exlamation mark, that is a clue that there is a soldier    |
|      on one of the squares touching the green exclamation mark.       |
|      Finally, the soldier formations which you have completely        |
|      destroyed are marked with yellow spheres. After viewing these    |
|      markers you will be able to make an informed decision! (^o^)     |
|      This game is fun with online play! You can enter the online      |
|      game if you have the Sega of Japan authorization files on        |
|      your dreamcast~ (these are from the Dream Passport browsers)     |
|      Unfortunately, the developer 45XLV (FortyFive) has decided to    |
|      close their online servers on May 10, 2001. (T-T) But don't      |
|      despair! There is still some time to play this game online!!     |
|      You should also know that you must unlock the online mode in     |
|      this game! (@. @) When you arrive at the map, you can see a      |
|      large tower on the hill. That is the Internet Gateway! When      |
|      you go there, you must battle Sister Tanetto (tournament         |
|      network) as she is the "guardian of connection". Once you        |
|      defeat her (she is so difficult! >.<) she will give you          |
|      access to the internet mode! And then you can play with many     |
|      people from around Japan as a reward~ You can also play this     |
|      game with a friend though~ But it will only work if each         |
|      player has their own SEGA VMU (with screen) because that is      |
|      the only way to hide your battle field from your opponent!       |
|      This game features cute anime characters and happy melodies,     |
|      and leaves a very nice impression! The snow-world which you      |
|      enter is so calm and sincere... (^.~^) If you like strategic     |
|      gameplay that is also a beautiful artwork, you will love         |
|      Tsuushin Taisen Logic Battle Daisessen!                          |
